BUILD
======================
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug ..
make

cd ..

RUN - Basic commands to run BFD using Docker: 
======================
./run_bfd.sh build
======================
./run_bfd.sh up
======================
./run_bfd.sh down
======================

For more options, like adding sessions and debugging, see:
./run_bfd.sh help





   
